---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About — Peculiar Engineer"
	description="About Minor Keith and Peculiar Engineer — a working engineer documenting every Linux, Cloudflare, and DevOps fix so you never have to Google the same problem twice."
	pubDate={new Date('2026-06-05')}
	showDate={false}
	heroImage={AboutHeroImage}
>
	<p class="whoami"><span class="prompt">~/$</span> whoami</p>

	<p>
		Hi, I'm <strong>Minor Keith</strong> — an engineer with a memory like a
		<code>/tmp</code> directory: whatever I figured out last week is usually gone by
		Monday. Peculiar Engineer is where I write it all down so I don't have to Google
		the same error for the tenth time.
	</p>

	<p>
		Everything here is documentation of something I actually ran into and solved — the
		command that finally worked, the cryptic error that ate an afternoon, the config
		flag buried on page nine of some forum thread — plus the tricks I pick up and the
		new tools and software I stumble onto along the way. Real steps, real reasoning, no
		fluff. It's written first for future-me at 2&nbsp;a.m., but if it saves you a search
		too, even better.
	</p>

	<p>
		If a guide saved you some time, or you spot something that's gone stale, feel free
		to reach out. Thanks for stopping by.
	</p>
</Layout>

<style>
	.whoami {
		font-family: var(--font-mono);
		color: var(--sys-dim);
		margin-bottom: 1.5em;
	}
	.whoami .prompt {
		color: var(--sys-fg);
		font-weight: 700;
	}
</style>
